query:
-- TPC 20

select
        s.name,
        s.address
from
        supplier s,
        nation n
where
        s.suppkey in (
                select
                        ps.suppkey
                from
                        partsupp ps
                where
                        ps.partkey in (
                                select
                                        p.partkey
                                from
                                        part p
                                where
                                        p.name like 'thistle%'
                        )
                        and ps.availqty > (
                                select
                                        0.5 * sum(l.quantity)
                                from
                                        lineitem l
                                where
                                        l.partkey = ps.partkey
                                        and l.suppkey = ps.suppkey
                                        and l.shipdate >= date '1993-01-01'
                                        and l.shipdate < date '1993-01-01' + interval '1' year
                        )
        )
        and s.nationkey = n.nationkey
        and n.name = 'ETHIOPIA'
order by
        s.name
